    guide:itemIndex 1^^xsd:integer ; # Section 5.2 structure implies order, though exact numbers not explicit in text for all items. I will use inferred indices based on list position or leave generic if strict index required? `guide:itemIndex` is xsd:integer. I'll assign sequential integers to represent the thematic units listed (1-7).
    guide:syllabusDescription "Introducción al estudio de la biomecánica, ciencias del deporte y definición."@en .

